Xagga [[Dhaqaale|dhaqaalaha]], '''isku xidhka Gini''' ( {{IPAc-en|ˈ|dʒ|iː|n|i}} {{Respell|JEE|nee}} ), oo sidoo kale loo yaqaan '''index''' '''Gini ama saamiga Gini''', waa cabbir kala firdhisanaan xisaabeed oo loogu talagalay in lagu matalo sinnaan la'aanta dakhliga ama sinnaan la'aanta hantida qaranka ama waddan kooxda bulshada. Isku-xidhka Gini waxa sameeyay xisaabiyaha iyo cilmiga bulshada Corrado Gini.
